{
 "name": "RPlog_Simon_and_Karrde",
 "title": "Simon and Karrde",
 "summary": "In a quiet, wind-swept alley off the commerce area of Talon Karrde's asteroid colony, the smuggler chief Karrde seeks out the Telgossian Selas Simon Sezirok to mend their fractious relationship and ask his help. After clearing past misunderstandings -- Simon clarifies he left the Dark Jedi Cort Stasus to free Jessalyn Valios, not to threaten Karrde -- the two find common ground and turn to business: locating the Death Star. Simon refuses to use the Force to invade minds but offers to capture and hold prisoners for interrogation and suggests the strong-willed Jessalyn may be better suited to the search. Trading their views on whether they are players or pieces in a galactic game, the wary pair agree to stay in contact through a secure office Karrde will provide, attach Simon's group to his organization for cover, and part as cautious new allies, leaving separately to avoid suspicion.",
